[I] Libraries and daemons to implement basic email handling

[T] Akonadi Mime is a library that effectively bridges the type-agnostic API of
[T] the Akonadi client libraries and the domain-specific KMime library. It
[T] provides jobs, models and other helpers to make working with emails through
[T] Akonadi easier.

[U] https://invent.kde.org/pim/akonadi-mime

